*At*Stepper.Button.Height:			1
*At*Stepper.lessV.Style:			uparrow
*At*Stepper.moreV.Style:			downarrow
*At*Stepper.lessH.Style:			leftarrow
*At*Stepper.moreH.Style:			rightarrow

! Button 

