*At*Button.BackgroundRGB:			defaultBorder
*At*Button.HighlightRGB:			defaultBorderHi
*At*Button.Style:				textinside

! Label 

*At*Label.Depth:				1
*At*Label.Margin:				2
*At*Label.Style:				textinside

